description:
Pope Tweets Mary is "Star of the Sea" - On July 9, 2017, Pope Francis tweeted that Mary is the “Star of the Sea,” and that we should look to her for “motherly protection.” Wrong. Jesus Christ Himself is the Star (see Revelation 22:17) of heaven, earth, and the seas. We must look to Him daily. He alone can protect us and help us in our struggles with sin, self, and Satan.
